==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inventive
<hw>In*vent"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>inventif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Able and apt to invent; quick at
contrivance; ready at expedients; <as>as, an <ex>inventive</ex> head or
genius</as>.</def> <au>Dryden.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>In*vent"ive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>In*vent"ive*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inventor</ent>⟦br⟧
